{"tid":335841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那又爆】酒樓大爆炸多人浴血 目擊者：樓上大廈玻璃全碎","createTime":"2017-07-26T02:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T07:19:26.000Z","uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"571345e7b49693dcdfdf5f4a3bec7eb4b3263902","tid":335841,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170726/57002934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170726%2F57002934&d=ZZgZ4TDTz8rabxIAk%2BwzNv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3383380c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170726%2F57002934&h=812ce6df\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170726/57002934</a><br />\n<br />\n山東濟南一間位於一商住大廈地下的酒樓，發生疑似煤氣爆炸，事發於今早接近7時，銀豐唐郡荷花園15號樓一間「明旭酒樓」發生爆炸，波及毗鄰的東側酒樓，對面商舖的玻璃亦震碎。據悉，現場最少有7至8人受傷，消防車已抵達現場救援。從現場影片可見，有人一身血地被用擔架抬走。<br />\n<br />\n有當地居民表示，事發時正準備上班，突然聽見一聲巨響，初時以為是打雷，連窗玻璃都震的晃動不停。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸導致酒樓一、二樓的牆被炸倒，但沒有明火，酒樓樓上的整棟住宅大樓的玻璃都碎了。酒樓瓦礫飛至30多米左右的車道上，馬路對面有兩個單位玻璃也碎，停在樓周圍的車玻璃也碎了。警方正在調查事發原因，有屋苑業主稱可能是煤氣罐爆炸。"},{"pid":"601362d1dfa663cf461d0110d1ee4f9a8c8d664d","tid":335841,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:19:22.000Z","msg":"真係咩都爆"},{"pid":"a1f6b9d82bc8e507359992da3e520630b33f45f5","tid":335841,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf09721cb89fd9327a2dd817b3e042e1f5bd71f4","tid":335841,"uid":57110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6z4vg1ip\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6z4vg1ip&h=b29a8cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3243c0a834cb8d53ee615e3ef92bacc9947d6b4b","tid":335841,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislik